[/url][/size][/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup

[size=6]Recommended:[/size]

[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35303/?]Female Facial Animation
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509]Familiar Faces[/url][/size]  (if you want to try them as your follower, cuz idont have the skills to make one)

[size=6]Installation:[/size]

[size=3]Step-1. Download my mod and place it at Data/SKSE/plugins/CharGen/Presets

[size=3]Step-[/size]2. Start Skyrim using SKSE loader

[size=3]Step-[/size]3. Load any working save file or start a newgame

[size=3]Step-[/size]4. Open the console " ~ "

[size=3]Step-[/size]5. Type "showracemenu"

[size=3]Step-[/size]6. Select the Orc Race. (if you dont want to be an Orc choose other Race, then use "Sculpt" inside RaceMenu
            then click "Import Head" choose "Orc Ivhara Head" do this after "Step-7 and Step-8".)

[size=3]Step-[/size]7. Look for "Preset" inside RaceMenu

[size=3]Step-[/size]8. Press F9, then click "Orc Ivhara or Orc Ivhara Origin"

[size=3]Step-[/size]9. Play! have fun... :D
[/size][size=4]

[/size][size=4][size=5][/size][/size][center][size=4][size=5]Feel free to use All My Presets
in your Mods or any mods[/size]
